WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.220
CHAPTER XI.

00:09.860 --> 00:16.960
A false balance is abomination to the Lord, But a just wait is his delight.

00:18.080 --> 00:23.520
When pride cometh, then cometh shame, But with the lowly is wisdom.

00:23.520 --> 00:30.680
The integrity of the upright shall guide them, But the perverseness of transgressors shall

00:30.680 --> 00:38.180
destroy them. Riches profit not in the day of wrath, But righteousness delivereth from death.

00:39.660 --> 00:45.740
The righteousness of the perfect shall direct his way, But the wicked shall fall by his own

00:45.740 --> 00:53.500
wickedness. The righteousness of the upright shall deliver them, But transgressors shall be taken

00:53.500 --> 01:01.900
in their own naughtiness. When a wicked man dieth, his expectation shall perish, and the hope of

01:01.900 --> 01:07.860
unjust men perisheth. The righteous is delivered out of trouble, and the wicked cometh in his

01:07.860 --> 01:14.960
stead. An hypocrite with his mouth destroyeth his neighbor, but through knowledge shall the just be

01:14.960 --> 01:21.980
delivered. When it goeth well with the righteous, the city rejoiceth, and when the wicked perish,

01:21.980 --> 01:29.840
there is shouting. By the blessing of the upright the city is exalted, but it is overthrown by the

01:29.840 --> 01:36.460
mouth of the wicked. He that is void of wisdom despiseth his neighbor, but a man of understanding

01:36.460 --> 01:44.820
holdeth his peace. A tale-bearer reveals secrets, but he that is of a faithful spirit concealeth

01:44.820 --> 01:51.740
the matter. Where no counsel is, the people fall, but in the multitude of counselors there is safety.

01:51.740 --> 02:00.940
He that is surety for a stranger shall smart for it, and he that hateth suretorship is sure. A gracious

02:00.940 --> 02:08.680
woman retaineth honor, and strong men retain riches. The merciful man doeth good to his own soul,

02:09.220 --> 02:17.060
but he that is cruel trebleth his own flesh. The wicked worketh a deceitful work, but to him that

02:17.060 --> 02:26.740
righteousness shall be a sure reward. As righteousness tendeth to life, so he that pursueth evil pursueth

02:26.740 --> 02:34.860
it to his own death. They that are of a foward heart are abomination to the Lord, but such as

02:34.860 --> 02:42.040
are upright in their way are his delight. Though hand joined in hand, the wicked shall not be

02:42.040 --> 02:50.740
punished, but the seed of the righteous shall be delivered. As a jewel of gold in a swine snout,

02:51.500 --> 02:58.100
so is a fair woman which is without discretion. The desire of the righteous is only good,

02:58.700 --> 03:05.000
but the expectation of the wicked is wrath. There is that scattereth, and yet increaseth,

03:05.000 --> 03:13.100
and there is that withholdeth more than his meat, but it tendeth to poverty. The liberal soul shall

03:13.100 --> 03:21.400
be made fat, and he that watereth shall be watered also himself. He that withholdeth corn,

03:21.800 --> 03:29.230
the people shall curse him, but blessing shall be upon the head of him that selleth it. He that

03:29.230 --> 03:37.970
seeketh good procureth favor, but he that seeketh mischief it shall come unto him. He that trusteth

03:37.970 --> 03:44.810
in his riches shall fall, but the righteous shall flourish as a branch. He that trebleth his own

03:44.810 --> 03:56.670
house shall inherit the wind, and the fool shall be servant to the wise of heart. The fruit of the

03:56.670 --> 04:04.210
is wise. Behold, the righteous shall be recompensed in the earth, much more the wicked in the sinner.

